Non.

284
00:17:03,027 --> 00:17:06,023
On n'irait pas bien ensemble.

285
00:17:09,907 --> 00:17:11,651
Je dois vous dire,
Mlle Sanders,

286
00:17:11,865 --> 00:17:14,402
