424
00:26:51,238 --> 00:26:54,532
Moi ? Pourquoi t'en es si sûr ?

425
00:26:54,658 --> 00:26:56,782
Tu es l'homme volant. Whoosh!

426
00:26:57,326 --> 00:27:00,703
